WYSIWYM.libraries
Class LinguisticTerms

java.lang.Object
  WYSIWYM.libraries.LinguisticTerms

public class LinguisticTerms
extends Object

LinguisticTerms contains linguistic constants used in the NLG-package, such as 'subject', 'noun', etc. It also contains terms for ellipsis structures and morphology.

Version:
1.00 2006/11/13, 1.4 2008/07/30
Author:
Feikje Hielkema

isConstituent

public static boolean isConstituent(String syn,
                                    String dep)
Checks whether the the given combination of syntactic and dependency label is a constituent (e.g. NP) or not (e.g. noun).

Parameters:
syn - Syntactic category
dep - Dependency label
Returns:
true if this is a constituent
